  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-92e447bb-6721-44e9-9a71-89c11fe3d087\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3d2a7e4c-9f5c-4108-84e2-87913aed7678\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e967a8ad-e68f-469c-8849-fe066945e63f\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Story Boarding DAY 20</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-1fe9fb02-4b80-4e27-861a-ca0955e7b2a0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8cdf7fc8-b28f-4598-b092-d1b5b4515c9b\" style=\"color:#0095e9;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e778d04e-477a-4b98-a3f3-bd81d9b5b16d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b5d67462-c282-4551-8d81-ced0b34c0054\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>[요소정리]</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-50a0db62-a831-4c11-9861-99fa9e282608\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b6d4097f-628a-49c4-b5cf-b562e58800fa\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>앞으로 7일간은 주문에 필요한 인쇄의 기본적인 요소를 정리하는 시간을 갖도록 하겠습니다. 27년의 인쇄 노하우를 가진 제가 좋은 자료를 만들기 위해 본격적으로 정리한 것이니 잘 읽어보시고 인쇄 주문이나 발주시 참고하셨으면 합니다. 기본적인 요소 정리가 마무리 되어 갑니다. 최종 프로세스를 정리하고 내일은 스토리보드 작업을 위한 ppt작업에 들어갑니다. 시작합니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2cbf8985-e3fb-4967-96e7-b5c2c08bc88d\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-16c23a8d-a3e6-4860-a142-018875a484eb\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-e47777d0-1baa-4b2f-869a-e4fdb0c605ef\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-657fba67-3125-4a4d-9498-39352857891f\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-70847c1c-957c-41de-b7f9-f82b1c7b2f41\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-706990de-e1f3-40a8-9185-3b423cc11758\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>제 사전에 실패는 있습니다. 하지만 시도가 없지는 않을 겁니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-735cddba-e74d-417d-8ec8-e6b4c5d333a8\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2a27883a-bd27-4304-92ce-e995686a7dc0\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>\"</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4fbf4a4b-0f28-4360-a7c0-b16b6c301a46\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-884c1c64-dc06-4224-a0cd-ed9c3123acae\" style=\"color:#ff5f45;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-5da9f690-34de-4df8-b36c-19f1ffd81a99\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-35b83975-d28c-4947-90b7-c0009897d96c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-104628c1-9cf9-49b6-9421-b35e499ef0b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>요소별 주문 프로세스 정리</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-adfe437d-e640-4b39-8b96-fd7c4e91f1e2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-674b5ed8-2000-420c-9013-2b98c4ddbab0\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-463d66cb-d6e7-41a9-ad0e-3f8eafaee368\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트에서 우리는 고객에게서 무엇을 받을건지 어떤 정보를 물어 볼건지를 결정하고 처리하는 과정을 커뮤니케이션 하겠습니다. 7일간 언급한 인쇄주문 요소중에 어떤건 변경할 수 있고 어떤건 수정이 불가능한지를 파악하고 고객입장에서 정말로 간단한 사이트를 만드는것이 중요하다고 생각합니다. 어려운 인쇄 주문을 가장 심플하고 가장 효과적으로 처리하는 고민의 과정에 있습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a5e95ad1-f908-48fc-91d3-492c0f486c09\" style=\"line-height:1.8;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanumgothic se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-279fe03e-f857-46ea-8030-2a16a26d9b4d\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-78254916-95ee-48c0-b1d9-5fe6adbb2cca\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222899481807/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-479ca5a2-04ad-4dd1-a2a6-2136b7b85ecc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dd02a9ec-6426-4279-a64c-e7f8f54e3efb\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-444aaf87-5baa-4091-9d01-707c9dab603e\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7115af94-dd17-46d4-bce2-e6e7dfe59781\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d62139c1-132d-43d6-950a-a625af010632\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">이 과정을 다음과 같이 하겠습니다. 자신의 맞는 템플릿을 검색하는 방법 4가지입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-256e9d8c-37d2-49cc-98db-0201060f4ccf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-984a2058-4335-448e-a2bb-a6065737040d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-131d8fd2-f205-4bb0-8928-4fe9527e88b4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7f3aa3b3-55d1-427c-80e1-188b04e492c1\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>템플릿 검색으로 선택</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-78125556-a8e3-4e95-9d47-bb48998f4ae9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222899481807/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2b69bc03-59b4-4485-98a1-6d558d35254d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-227f679e-3a96-4dec-a009-e88aaa163ffa\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-87240473-d710-47bf-9e49-07a64ec4bb13\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니 템플릿에 태그 기능을 추가합니다. 이 태그는 그 템플릿에 맞는 디자인과 사양을 찾아 줄 것입니다. 예를들어 <span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#쇼핑백</span> <span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#병원</span> 을 검색한다면 다음 태그에 등록된 디자인이 나올겁니다. 만약 등록된 디자인이 없으면 메인창에는 아무것도 표시되지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f0c1fa14-99f2-43ec-a7a4-e78d03908aef\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e2ce85d4-d5c7-4667-aa64-85f35e256af4\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-dba03cc3-a834-4025-9b5f-2e4d74d26b08\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-babb1143-e832-4597-87b1-7580a9cb345f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-de4cc8f6-5d5c-41c6-b322-cdcd9ba1b152\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2c9bcb68-bbba-486b-b287-2df5311b5124\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>카테고리 분류로 선택</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8e38fd01-3412-4483-94fa-fc9c28ef96f9\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222899481807/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f4f86cd-3629-4725-ad36-7171b443bd1a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-1f5e5347-218e-446c-a65f-32d3d79148f8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-e0a8a4ca-8dd8-4e78-bb8e-9585c4c00f3f\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">기본 카테고리로 검색할 수 있습니다. 이 조건은 다른 검색과 And 조건이 됩니다. 명함을 선택하고 검색으로 조건을 선택하면 명함은 <span class=\"__se-hash-tag\">#명함</span> 이 되어 있다는 의미입니다. 카테고리를 넣은 이유는 일반적으로 대 분류를 선택하고 결정하는 고객을 위한 것입니다. 카테고리를 선택하면 메인창에는 선택된 카테고리만 표현됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-7fe93dea-c97e-46ff-9555-2e81055ee2e5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d0e34cfe-440f-4117-8959-f8a4d1c22a0a\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-bec617e9-a0b0-490c-b33b-81ed9827e243\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-db3a0cca-87aa-472a-a608-53ebe1f9fd59\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-0b8b40c5-0543-4fe1-adaa-41cf2c682ec1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b354f986-cd02-4d0e-bccd-33769891eb9b\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>디자인 템플릿으로 선택</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-005323da-7964-459a-a4b9-2eb07cff94dc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222899481807/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-555e269f-24a7-48ab-b2f5-3607887a9893\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-dbb7574f-6d00-4dc1-ba43-38b5a3ae2469\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-2ddf1171-4b1e-446e-9854-7ae896cb9089\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">메인창에 있는 디자인을 시각적으로 보고 선택하는 방법입니다. 검색과 카테고리 선택에 모두 적용을 받습니다. 고객은 시각적으로 표현된 디지인 이미지를 보고 그 템플릿을 선택하게 됩니다. 더 자세한 사항은 클릭 후 확인 할 수 있고 상세보기 표시 창을 통해 미리 검색하고 클릭할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ed471287-d62a-4b96-aaf2-a1b1726f596c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ea6c7d37-6262-4f0c-9bb4-c67b7e920217\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line2\" id=\"SE-af9f9c85-b0c7-45b5-910a-25ef8a1b5173\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line2 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7ad01438-90c5-4c9d-8733-685f436ed732\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-247125b1-03fc-4bd8-89d8-ea228c6b9791\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4efae21a-b10a-4df9-9f91-80a1a394a557\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>상세보기로 선택</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-34e929ff-7c5f-4451-ae34-2c4a83580df3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222899481807/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5338d9f6-65e4-4519-932e-32881e6f6046\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a9d36a48-45a2-41dd-8595-1c569bbaf379\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7956187c-c834-440d-9677-1573bef8dd60\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">최종적으로 하단에 표시된 상세보기 창을 통해 확인할 수 있습니다. 이 창에는 이 템플릿의 템플릿명과 가장 중요한 태그 3개를 노출하여 고객에게 정보를 제공합니다. 이 정보까지 확인하고 클릭하면 견적요청창으로 이동됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-bde9bdb6-036a-4f75-9986-1b2889e9339f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b3ae08c1-61d8-435f-a55b-93bfe11f8233\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-m