bf08-1c64cc01103c\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>내 디자인</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ffcd518a-190f-4c31-89d1-65165a83aea2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222899481807/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-11167b6a-2b68-43b1-a0ac-1845efcd272d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-a2cb2d7c-a70c-45b6-b335-43b4b9f0c434\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-67f4cd73-a1da-40a5-9760-41b796095b9b\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">(주)파파스컴퍼니은 로그인하고 내가 디자인하고 주문한 템플릿을 빠르게 서칭해서 주문을 요청할 수 있습니다. 디자인이 변경된다면 디자인요청을 추가로 하고 그대로 주문하는 재주문이면 바로 신청해서 주문할 수 있습니다. 이 부분은 견적요청도 건너띄고 바로 주문하고 생산을 넘어가는 프로세스를 타게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-f200722b-fd29-4e24-9a50-c1486fed2773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-b9a6547f-364c-4b4c-a756-13a8e0bd42c6\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-92aabf0d-745f-4ed0-99d6-33cf2657a809\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-558db60d-d120-4107-ad28-acef73e3a826\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">단, 로그인을 하지 않았다면 로그인 유도창으로 넘어갑니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b35596a8-2c24-44be-b3a0-9dcff37bdb86\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/222899481807/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cd165aff-e2c6-46f3-b967-347f3ab44d31\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1f562d88-8c27-4fcd-84bf-1e71b7ef0bc0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-39cae040-d55d-4a62-8080-397d5930b850\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-4fa29f28-ccf9-4391-97ea-7595e33263a7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-justify\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b36540df-3f32-4ee3-bea5-4a7d6fb25882\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-T