e-style-unset\" id=\"SE-67d3617e-a42d-4349-bbd5-c520fc640264\" style=\"color:#000000;background-color:#ffffff;\">주문시 고객의 변경되는 정보를 받아서 디자인을 수정하는 부분을 만드는 란입니다. 로고나 사진의 변경은 짜로 업로드 파일이나 텍스트로 요청해야 하며 우리는 기본 템플릿의 글자만을 수정하는 작업을 제공하겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-ee5440ff-75bc-4280-b8a1-690f962ec1e0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ad4a686e-0bfa-4013-b623-14e1a6cb8367\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-933f17cb-751f-4127-8572-7751d2dc1dd0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ad077cf9-55d8-4223-aa3c-393b870c7806\" style=\"color:#000000;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_line\" id=\"SE-b8bb9995-f4d6-4b30-bb0c-604d0a1e2f0e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_line\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1dd8edd7-30fd-45c6-8d92-b2f2d61d68fd\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-e7c106e8-d5ed-436e-8f1e-4b978903bf10\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>다음 글의 내용</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ff1cb542-794a-4340-9bf2-592104efc910\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-justify\" id=\"SE-d836795e-d324-4a7b-8a63-5c48efc6f1d5\" style=\"line-height:1.5;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanumgothic se-style-unset\" id=\"